  "label": "Ashlight Stores",
  "description": "Ashlight Stores is a narrow, gasketed chamber of basalt block and riveted sheet-metal, set behind a pressure-rated hatch to preserve the canteen’s ash seal. Steel shelving rises to the ceiling baffles, holding ration tins, solvent drums, and stacked kegs secured by grounded chains against Vespera Tertius’ electrostatic charge. A grated trench drain runs the centerline for washdown, and the air carries the metallic bite of disinfectant over stale dust. Violet-glass utility lamps maintain the bruise-colored cast that defines the taproom beyond.",
